      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://img363.imageshack.us/img363/4915/windowslivewriterjpg.png&#34; width=&#34;240&#34; height=&#34;156&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Já uso há bastante tempo o &lt;a href=&#34;http://download.live.com/writer&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Windows Live Writer&lt;/a&gt; como ferramenta de publicação nos meus blogs, e vou sempre procurando plugins que me possam facilitar a tarefa de criação de posts.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Faço este post não só para divulgação de alguns plugins, mas também para ficar como minha referência no caso de me esquecer de algum quando precisar de reinstalar o PC.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Seguem então alguns plugins sem qualquer ordem de importância:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveItemDetail.aspx?li=07c1dabd-accc-411f-bae0-ddef160067a9&amp;bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Facebook Live Writer Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveItemDetail.aspx?li=d9449418-e352-4850-8398-458edece8e74&amp;bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;On the fly Zip and attach Live Writer Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveItemDetail.aspx?li=bbb14b2a-0250-4513-a942-cb99a3459ab9&amp;bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Tag Generator&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveItemDetail.aspx?li=e5a2ba98-e2a9-4083-a86f-c20a87e9253d&amp;bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Imtech MSDN Reference Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveItemDetail.aspx?li=6ba7122b-56aa-4651-a7ab-613359a31986&amp;bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;SnagIt Screen Capture Plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveItemDetail.aspx?li=f5eb0e56-0132-4d3e-95c8-d43cd2c62688&amp;bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;SkyDrive Attachment plugin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/liveitemdetail.aspx?li=1f57bd9b-a692-4593-9e9e-e2962d9c0eee&amp;l=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Insert Code for Windows Live Writer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://code.google.com/p/imageshackwriterplugin/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;ImageShack&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Podem encontrar mais plugins na &lt;a href=&#34;http://gallery.live.com/results.aspx?bt=9&amp;pl=8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Windows Live Gallery&lt;/a&gt;, e caso tenham algum para recomendar é só indicar nos comentários.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
